        I_VE_GOT_TO_KEEP_ON_GOING_STARTING                                            = 10090,  -- I've got to keep on going--starting with these seeds right here.
        BUT_HE_S_NOT_THE_ONLY_ONE_I                                                   = 10091,  -- But he's not the only one I have to thank. You have done me a great service as well.
        THIS_IS_LONG_OVERDUE_AND_I_APOLOGIZE_FOR                                      = 10092,  -- This is long overdue, and I apologize for my tardiness.
        I_ONLY_HOPE_THAT_YOU_WILL_FIND_IT                                             = 10093,  -- I only hope that you will find it an appropriate reward.
        I_SWEAR_MY_EYES_ARE_STARTING_TO_FAIL                                          = 10094,  -- I swear, my eyes are starting to fail me after reading so many reports of pioneers falling victim to...rather unconventional traps set throughout the wilderness.
        BY_ALTANA_S_GOOD_GRACES_I_KNOW_THAT                                           = 10095,  -- By Altana's good graces, I know that nefarious Blackthorn Coven is behind it all, but what could they possibly hope to gain by doing this...?
        BREAK_THE_SILENCE_WHAT_S_THE_BLACKTHORN_COVEN                                 = 10096,  -- Break the silence? What's the Blackthorn Coven? No, it's not my place.
        THE_BLACKTHORN_COVEN_IS_A_BAND_OF_THREE                                       = 10097,  -- The Blackthorn Coven is a band of three of the cruelest enchantresses to ever assail Vana'diel.
        THEY_NEST_DEEP_WITHIN_THE_WOODS_PERFORMING_STRANGE                            = 10098,  -- They nest deep within the woods, performing strange rituals and subjecting all who dare enter their domain to unspeakable horrors--and such incidents have been on the rise of late.
        WE_HAVE_A_PONTIFICATION_OF_OUR_FINEST_EXORCISTS                               = 10099,  -- We have a pontification of our finest exorcists scouring the land for them, but I would still exercise caution should your travels take you wealdward.
        EXCUSE_ME_GOOD_SIR_FAIR_LADY                                                  = 10100,  -- Excuse me, good sir/fair lady]!
        I_M_TERRIBLY_SORRY_TO_BOTHER_YOU_OUT                                          = 10101,  -- I'm terribly sorry to bother you out of the blue like this, but my name is Nashu. I'm also an exorcist...or at least one in training.
        I_COULDN_T_HELP_BUT_OVERHEAR_YOUR_CONVERSATION                                = 10102,  -- I couldn't help but overhear your conversation regarding the Blackthorn Coven.
        TO_TELL_THE_TRUTH_MANY_VETERAN_EXORCISTS_WITH                                 = 10103,  -- To tell the truth, many veteran exorcists with a storied history of service to Altana think it would be best to leave the Coven to their own devices for the time being.
        THE_ORDER_OF_WEATHERSPOON_IS_STAUNCHLY_OPPOSED_TO                             = 10104,  -- The Order of Weatherspoon is staunchly opposed to the colonization of Ulbuka, so they advocate maintaining this coincidental alliance.
        I_HOWEVER_CANNOT_ABIDE_THE_SUFFERING_OF_MY                                    = 10105,  -- I, however, cannot abide the suffering of my fellow man!
        AS_AN_EXORCIST_IT_IS_MY_DUTY_TO                                               = 10106,  -- As an exorcist, it is my duty to bring the heavy hammer of justice down upon these mavens of madness, these harlots of heresy!
        IT_CERTAINLY_WON_T_BE_AN_EASY_TASK                                            = 10107,  -- It certainly won't be an easy task. Ensnaring even one adept practitioner of the dark arts would fell a man, but three... To be honest, I don't think I'm skilled enough to capture them myself.
        THEREFORE_WOULD_WOULD_YOU_BE_SO_KIND_AS                                       = 10108,  -- Therefore, would... Would you be so kind as to lend me a hand in this endeavor?
        LEND_A_HAND_WITH_PLEASURE_TO_THIS_TWERP                                       = 10109,  -- Lend a hand? With pleasure. To this twerp? Never.
        I_I_KNOW_I_SHOULDN_T_HAVE_EVEN                                                = 10110,  -- I...I know... I shouldn't have even asked. Sorry for so blatantly overstepping my bounds.
        MAKE_SURE_NOT_TO_BE_CAUGHT_UNAWARES_SHOULD                                    = 10111,  -- Make sure not to be caught unawares should you venture into the weald. There is no way to tell whether we will have captured the Blackthorn Coven by the time you enter.
        Y_YOU_RE_THAT_ADVENTURER_FROM_BEFORE_OVER                                     = 10112,  -- Y-you're that adventurer from before! Over here, over here!
        YOU_WOULDN_T_HAPPEN_TO_HAVE_CHANGED_YOUR                                      = 10113,  -- You wouldn't happen to have changed your mind about....you know...the thing, would you?
        I_GIVE_YOU_MY_UNDYING_GRATITUDE_BEFORE_I                                      = 10114,  -- I give you my undying gratitude! Before I get too excited, though, I should probably ask your name.
        IS_IT_WELL_I_M_UTTERLY_OVERJOYED_TO                                           = 10115,  -- %, is it? Well, %, I'm utterly overjoyed to have made your acquaintance!
        GETTING_DOWN_TO_BUSINESS_THE_LAST_CONFIRMED_SIGHTING                          = 10116,  -- Getting down to business... The last confirmed sighting of the Blackthorn Coven I've heard about was in %, around what corresponds to grid J-6 on your map. That seems like as good a place as any to start looking.
        MIGHT_YOU_BE                                                                  = 10117,  -- Might you be %?
        NASHU_ASKED_ME_TO_RELAY_THIS_MESSAGE_TO                                       = 10118,  -- Nashu asked me to relay this message to you. It simply states, Meet me at J-6 in %. Whatever could be going through that boy's head?
        HE_KNOWS_FULL_WELL_THE_BLACKTHORN_COVEN_HAS                                   = 10119,  -- He knows full well the Blackthorn Coven has been spotted there numerous times. Should you choose to search him out, may Altana's guiding light envelop you in its protective glow.
        GOOD_TIDINGS_TO_YOU                                                           = 10120,  -- Good tidings to you, %.
        NASHU_TOLD_ME_ALL_ABOUT_YOUR_LITTLE_ADVENTURE                                 = 10121,  -- Nashu told me all about your little adventure and how it ended in failure. I cannot say that I am surprised--the Blackthorn Coven wouldn't be the wickedest witches in the west if any wide-eyed novice could capture them.
        I_MUST_SAY_THOUGH_THE_NUMBER_OF_PIONEERS                                      = 10122,  -- I must say, though, the number of pioneers falling victim to traps throughout the jungle has absolutely plummeted.
        DON_T_GET_ANY_IDEAS_GETTING_INVOLVED_WITH                                     = 10123,  -- Don't get any ideas. Getting involved with those harpies will only result in him--or you--getting hurt.
        ID_10124                                                                      = 10124,  -- %! %! %!
        HOW_SERENDIPITOUS_OF_ME_TO_BUMP_INTO_YOU                                      = 10125,  -- How serendipitous of me to bump into you.
        I_JUST_BECAME_PRIVY_TO_SOME_MOST_SCANDALOUS                                   = 10126,  -- I just became privy to some most scandalous gossip. Will you please lend an ear?
        APPARENTLY_THOSE_MOTHERS_OF_MALEVOLENCE_HAVE_ENTERED_INTO                     = 10127,  -- Apparently those mothers of malevolence have entered into negotiations with the only clan more bloodthirsty than they...the Velkk!
        THESE_REPTILIAN_DEGENERATES_ARE_KNOWN_TO_WADDLE_AROUND                        = 10128,  -- These reptilian degenerates are known to waddle around the crevasses of %, indiscriminately attacking on sight all who infringe upon their territory.
        THEY_RELENTLESSLY_TEAR_THEIR_PREY_APART_WITH_THEIR                            = 10129,  -- They relentlessly tear their prey apart with their powerful jaws for the sheer joy of killing, and then leave the remaining shards of bone and strips of flesh to rot upon the ground. Normally, no one would ever encroach upon their settlement.
        WHAT_WOULD_KEEP_A_RUTHLESS_BAND_OF_MURDERERS                                  = 10130,  -- What would keep a ruthless band of murderers like the Velkk from trying to slaughter these witches--who are still technically people--with no questions asked?
        PERHAPS_OUR_FAILED_ATTEMPT_TO_CAPTURE_THE_SORCEROUS                           = 10131,  -- Perhaps our failed attempt to capture the sorcerous trio in Yorcia Weald has come back to haunt us. Now that I mull this over, we never did hear what they wanted with % and %...
        OH_MY_COULD_WE_HAVE_INADVERTENTLY_AIDED_IN                                    = 10132,  -- Oh, my... Could we have inadvertently aided in the coven's nefarious deeds? If so, we have to find them and stop them before I suffer a theological crisis!
        HELP_FIND_THE_COVEN_OF_COURSE_FOR_ALTANA                                      = 10133,  -- Help find the coven? Of course, for Altana's sake! Um, Zaffeld told me to stay away. No, go have your theological crisis.
        SIGH_OF_COURSE_IT_IS_ALL_MY_FAULT                                             = 10134,  -- <Sigh> Of course. It is all my fault. When will I learn to leave the more incriminating details out of my reports?
        STILL_I_FIRMLY_BELIEVE_THAT_MY_KEEN_SENSE                                     = 10135,  -- Still, I firmly believe that my keen sense of justice will triumph over my bureaucratic shortcomings! In the name of all that is holy, %, I beseech your aid!
        I_I_SEE_MY_APOLOGIES_FOR_BURDENING_YOU                                        = 10136,  -- I...I see... My apologies for burdening you with such a request.
        GETTING_INVOLVED_WITH_THOSE_HARPIES_WILL_ONLY_RESULT                          = 10137,  -- Getting involved with those harpies will only result in him--or you--getting hurt.
        HAVE_YOU_DECIDED_TO_HELP_ME_DIG_UP                                            = 10138,  -- Have you decided to help me dig up what the Blackthorn Coven is planning? I am always in need of someone who has the Goddess's blessing, you know.
        THANK_YOU_IMMENSELY                                                           = 10139,  -- Thank you immensely!
        THE_TRIAD_OF_TERROR_RENDEZVOUSED_WITH_THE_VELKK                               = 10140,  -- The triad of terror rendezvoused with the Velkk in quadrant E-7 of %, if recent scouting reports are to be believed.
        MAYBE_THOSE_LAZY_LIZARDS_ARE_STILL_BASKING_IN                                 = 10141,  -- Maybe those lazy lizards are still basking in the glow of their successful negotiation. If you could head down there and put your ears to the ground, as it were, hopefully we can learn something of value.
        JUST_MAKE_SURE_YOU_DON_T_END_UP                                               = 10142,  -- Just make sure you don't end up six fulms under!
        NASHU_ASKED_ME_TO_REMIND_YOU_TO_MUSTER                                        = 10143,  -- Nashu asked me to remind you to muster at E-7 of % before he darted off.
        I_TRIED_TO_WARN_HIM_ABOUT_THE_FOOLISHNESS                                     = 10144,  -- I tried to warn him about the foolishness of his acts, but he simply muttered something about divine retribution. Listen to me--that boy's unstable, and you'll get into nothing but trouble if you keep chasing the Blackthorn Coven.
        WHAT_CAN_THE_COALITION_DO_FOR_YOU_TODAY                                       = 10145,  -- What can the coalition do for you today, good sir/lady]?
        YOU_SAY_THAT_ALIANNE_FROM_THE_ORDER_OF                                        = 10146,  -- You say that Alianne from the Order of Janniston would like our maester to investigate something for her?
        IS_THIS_SOME_KIND_OF_JOKE_IF_MARGRET                                          = 10147,  -- Is this some kind of joke? If Margret were to take on the work of every last citizen who wanted her aid, why...
        PEOPLE_THIRST_FOR_KNOWLEDGE_WEGELLION_AND_AS_THE                              = 10148,  -- People thirst for knowledge, Wegellion, and as the Scouts' Coalition maester, I feel a responsibility to aid our citizenry whenever I am able.
        BUT_YOU_WOULD_HAVE_ME_SHUT_THE_DOORS                                          = 10149,  -- But you would have me shut the doors to one in search of answers. What say you about this particular case?
        ESTEEMED_MAESTER_I_ONLY_MEAN_TO_SAY_THAT                                      = 10150,  -- Esteemed Maester, I only mean to say that we must carefully select our battles.
        YOUR_APPROACH_IS_CORRECT_INDEED_BUT_IT_IS                                     = 10151,  -- Your approach is correct, indeed--but it is not your place to make decisions for me.
        O_OF_COURSE_NOT_MAESTER                                                       = 10152,  -- O-of course not, Maester.
        PRAY_TELL_WHAT_WOULD_YOU_ASK_OF_ME                                            = 10153,  -- Pray tell, what would you ask of me?
        IT_S_ABOUT_THAT_YOUNG_MAN_THEN_I                                              = 10154,  -- It's about that young man, then? I suppose I should not be surprised. Truth be told, I have been continuing to investigate his case.
        I_DO_NOT_MIND_TAKING_ON_SOMETHING_ELSE                                        = 10155,  -- I do not mind taking on something else related to this incident, but I have one condition.
        I_CHANCED_UPON_A_VOLUME_OF_GREAT_INTEREST                                     = 10156,  -- I chanced upon a volume of great interest during my research.
        IT_WAS_OLD_AND_WORN_AND_THE_GREASE                                            = 10157,  -- It was old and worn, and the grease of a thousand fingers had smudged some parts so that it was nigh indecipherable.
        HOWEVER_I_HAVE_AN_IDEA_HOW_TO_RESTORE                                         = 10158,  -- However, I have an idea how to restore the work to legibility. All I would need is for you to bring me % and %.
        WITH_THE_TIME_WHICH_I_WOULD_HAVE_DEVOTED                                      = 10159,  -- With the time which I would have devoted to procuring those items, I can focus on finding some clue which might lead you to a cure.
        BUT_A_WORD_OF_WARNING_IF_YOU_WILL                                             = 10160,  -- But, a word of warning, if you will.
        SOME_THINGS_ARE_BETTER_LEFT_UNKNOWN                                           = 10161,  -- Some things...are better left unknown.
        MAESTER_MARGRET_HAS_PLEDGED_HER_SUPPORT_TO_YOUR                               = 10162,  -- Maester Margret has pledged her support to your cause.
        BRING_US_AND_THAT_SHE_MIGHT_CONTINUE_HER                                      = 10163,  -- Bring us % and % that she might continue her pursuits.
        I_SEE_YOU_VE_FULFILLED_OUR_MAESTER_S                                          = 10164,  -- I see you've fulfilled our maester's request.
        SHE_HAS_FOUND_A_PERSON_OF_INTEREST_IN                                         = 10165,  -- She has found a person of interest in the case we were discussing earlier.
        I_SEE_YOU_VE_RETURNED                                                         = 10166,  -- I see you've returned.
        THIS_TARU_FRIEND_OF_OURS_IS_ARI_BARALI                                        = 10167,  -- This Taru friend of ours is Ari-Barali. He is prone to put on airs and deliver flowers to my dear friend Svenja, and hence has some information that may be of use.
        WOULD_YOU_MIND_SHARING_WHAT_YOU_HAVE_LEARNED                                  = 10168,  -- Would you mind sharing what you have learned with my acquaintance?
        O_OF_COURSE                                                                   = 10169,  -- O-of course...
        YOU_SEE_EVERY_DAY_I_DELIVER_TO_MISTRESS                                       = 10170,  -- You see, every day I deliver % to Mistress Svenja...and try to suppress my accentaru so that she looks kindly on me.
        O_OH_I_LET_IT_SLIP_OUT_ALIANNE                                                = 10171,  -- O-oh! I let it slip out! Alianne is the one who always greets me, but one time, she was not there.
        AND_SO_I_WELL_I_KNOW_I_SHOULDN                                                = 10172,  -- And so, I...well...I know I shouldn't have done this, but...
        I_WENT_AROUND_BACK_AND_PEEKED_INTO_SVENJA                                     = 10173,  -- I went around back and peeked into Svenja's room.
        MISTRESS_SVENJA_YOU_CANNOT_POSSIBLY_MEAN_TO_ADMINISTER                        = 10174,  -- Mistress Svenja, you cannot possibly mean to administer this medicine!?
        IT_WAS_DERIVED_FROM_THE_WHICH_THE_PIONEER                                     = 10175,  -- It was derived from the %, which the pioneer brought back from Ulbuka!
        DO_YOU_KNOW_WHAT_THIS_MEANS_IF_THE                                            = 10176,  -- Do you know what this means? If the medicine works, it will provide more fodder for those pro-colonization cronies!
        WE_HAVE_OPPOSED_COLONIZATION_FROM_THE_VERY_OUTSET                             = 10177,  -- We have opposed colonization from the very outset, knowing that the best way to protect our fair nation is to remain within these walls.
        AND_THIS_YOUNG_MAN_WAS_HE_NOT_A                                               = 10178,  -- And this young man--was he not a pioneer? Was this disease not brought upon him by his own foolhardiness?
        I_TOO_FEAR_THAT_HE_FELL_ILL_DUE                                               = 10179,  -- I, too, fear that he fell ill due to something he found in the wilds.
        AND_WORSE_FORGING_FURTHER_AHEAD_MIGHT_VERY_WELL                               = 10180,  -- And worse, forging further ahead might very well lead to other, more vile sicknesses.
        IF_THAT_IS_SO_MISTRESS_YOU_OF_ALL                                             = 10181,  -- If that is so, Mistress, you of all people must certainly understand what we must do.
        I_SUPPOSE_THERE_IS_NO_HELPING_IT_LET                                          = 10182,  -- I suppose there is no helping it. Let us refrain from administering the medicine a little while and see how this plays out.
        AT_FIRST_I_WASN_T_SURE_WHAT_THEY                                              = 10183,  -- At first, I wasn't sure what they meant.
        BUT_THEN_I_REALIZED_THAT_THEY_WERE_CHOOSING                                   = 10184,  -- But then I realized that they were choosing not to help save a young man even though the means were right in front of them.
        THAT_ONE_SO_LOVELY_COULD_SAY_SOMETHING_SO                                     = 10185,  -- That one so lovely could say something so malicious...it shook me to my very core.
        IT_TOOK_GREAT_COURAGE_FOR_YOU_TO_SPEAK                                        = 10186,  -- It took great courage for you to speak out like this.
        WELL_MY_DEAR_PIONEER_YOU_NOW_HAVE_SOMETHING                                   = 10187,  -- Well, my dear pioneer, you now have something to go on.
        WHETHER_YOU_CHOOSE_TO_TELL_ALIANNE_OR_NOT                                     = 10188,  -- Whether you choose to tell Alianne or not is for you alone to determine.
        IT_IS_MY_JOB_TO_PROVIDE_THE_INFORMATION                                       = 10189,  -- It is my job to provide the information, not decide what to do with it.
        BUT_REMEMBER_THIS_A_STORY_IS_LIKE_A                                           = 10190,  -- But remember this: a story is like a gold coin--there are always two sides.
        DIFFICULT_THOUGH_IT_IS_TO_FORGET_ARI_BARALI                                   = 10191,  -- Difficult though it is to forget Ari-Barali's sordid tale, I'll make sure word of it never leaves my lips.
        MY_MY_MY_WHATEVER_SHALL_I_DO_WITH                                             = 10192,  -- My, my, my. Whatever shall I do with you, %? I hear you've been out trying to save the world from the Blackthorn Coven with Nashu again.
        I_SWEAR_MY_JAW_WILL_HAVE_TO_FALL                                              = 10193,  -- I swear my jaw will have to fall from its hinges before you listen to me about staying away from those vexing viragoes.
        HOWEVER_THAT_S_ALL_WATER_UNDER_BIG_BRIDGE                                     = 10194,  -- However, that's all water under Big Bridge now, for any chance you had to go plunging headfirst into thorny thickets will soon be over.
        SINCE_WE_VE_ASCERTAINED_THEIR_INVOLVEMENT_WITH_THE                            = 10195,  -- Since we've ascertained their involvement with the Velkk, Lord Vortimere has ordered some...adept landscapers to do a bit of pruning.
        AS_I_DO_NOT_BELIEVE_YOUR_PIONEER_S                                            = 10196,  -- As I do not believe your pioneer's badge certifies you as a groundskeeper, I suggest you stick to colonization and leave the dirty work to us.
        THERE_YOU_ARE_OH_FRIEND_OF_FRIENDS_I                                          = 10197,  -- There you are, oh friend of friends! I was just about to go off and parlay with those enchantresses and thought you might want to come along.
        TO_BE_HONEST_I_STILL_CANNOT_FATHOM_WHY                                        = 10198,  -- To be honest, I still cannot fathom why anyone would ever be willing to conspire with heathens as blasphemous as the Velkk. My face turns flush with anger at the mere thought of such an atrocity.
        HOWEVER_THE_FACT_REMAINS_THAT_THEY_SAVED_ME                                   = 10199,  -- However, the fact remains that they saved me from certain doom at Dho Gates.
        COULD_IT_NOT_BE_POSSIBLE_THAT_THEIR_SPINOUS                                   = 10200,  -- Could it not be possible that their spinous exteriors are only a facade covering their silky soft hearts? Perhaps all we need to fertilize a congenial relationship with our sylvan sorceresses is to talk with them.
        WHAT_DO_YOU_SAY                                                               = 10201,  -- What do you say, %?
        WHAT_DO_YOU_SAY_HOW_PERSPICACIOUS_OF_YOU                                      = 10202,  -- What do you say? How perspicacious of you. Has your brain turned to mulch!?
        WHEW_YOU_CANNOT_IMAGINE_HOW_COMFORTING_IT_IS                                  = 10203,  -- Whew, you cannot imagine how comforting it is to hear that someone of your prowess holds the same sentiments. My confidence has shot through the roof!
        NO_WONDER_MY_SUPERIORS_HAVE_ME_SWABBING_CHAMBER                               = 10204,  -- No wonder my superiors have me swabbing chamber pots instead of helping exorcise evil spirits...
        YET_EVEN_A_TENDERFOOT_LIKE_ME_HAS_SOMETHING                                   = 10205,  -- Yet even a tenderfoot like me has something to offer this cloister! One could even say that I, specifically because of my inexperience, bring new blood to the family!
        THEREFORE_I_WAS_THINKING_OF_RETURNING_TO_THE                                  = 10206,  -- Therefore, I was thinking of returning to the Blackthorn Coven what they gave us in our prior adventures.
        OF_COURSE_AS_A_MEMBER_LOYAL_TO_THE                                            = 10207,  -- Of course, as a member loyal to the Order of Weatherspoon, my first thought was to hand it over to my superiors...but such would amount to betrayal of the people who rescued me.
        INSTEAD_I_HAVE_DECIDED_TO_USE_THIS_OPPORTUNITY                                = 10208,  -- Instead, I have decided to use this opportunity to meet and show them of the error of their ways. My silver tongue will convince them to consort with the Velkk no more!
        SURELY_YOU_WILL_JOIN_ME_IN_MY_PURSUIT                                         = 10209,  -- Surely you will join me in my pursuit of justice, %, will you not?
        WILL_YOU_HELP_FINE_I_LL_GO_COUNT                                              = 10210,  -- Will you help? Fine, I'll go. Count me out, scout.
        OH_I_SEE_MAYBE_I_SHOULD_STOP_RELYING                                          = 10211,  -- Oh... I see... Maybe I should stop relying on you so much. I will never learn to stand on my own two feet by constantly grasping at your coattails.
        NOW_THAT_WE_VE_ASCERTAINED_THE_BLACKTHORN_COVEN                               = 10212,  -- Now that we've ascertained the Blackthorn Coven's involvement with the Velkk, Lord Vortimere has ordered some...adept landscapers to do a bit of pruning.
        HAVE_YOU_DECIDED_TO_HELP_ME_MEET_OUR                                          = 10213,  -- Have you decided to help me meet our arch-nemeses?
        IF_THEIR_PAST_BEHAVIOR_IS_ANYTHING_TO_GO                                      = 10214,  -- If their past behavior is anything to go by, they will surely be skulking about Yorcia Weald! Let us rendezvous within its thickets at what corresponds to J-6 on your map.
        I_COULD_BARELY_MAKE_OUT_WHAT_NASHU_SAID                                       = 10215,  -- I could barely make out what Nashu said as he rushed past like a man on a mission, but I did hear something about going to J-6 in Yorcia Weald.
        HOW_MANY_TIMES_DO_I_HAVE_TO_TELL                                              = 10216,  -- How many times do I have to tell you that-- ...You know what? If you haven't learned by now, I'm not going to say anything.
        IT_SEEMS_RRRIDICULOUS_THAT_ROBERTIOUX_OF_ALL_PEOPLE                           = 10217,  -- It seems rrridiculous that Robertioux, of all people, could do away with an undead like that.
        YES_I_COULD_HARDLY_BELIEVE_MY_EARS_WHEN                                       = 10218,  -- Yes, I could hardly believe my ears when I first heard the news. To think it was one of those ancient dullahans decked out in plate armor, too.
        EVEN_MENTIONING_THE_NAME_OF_THOSE_HEADLESS_RELICS                             = 10219,  -- Even mentioning the name of those headless relics makes me think of my history lessons about the Great Expedition. If they have truly reappeared en masse, then who other than us can Adoulin call upon to save it?
        OUR_DAYS_OF_SITTING_IDLY_BY_WATCHING_PIONEERS                                 = 10220,  -- Our days of sitting idly by watching pioneers pilfer all the prrrestige will finally be over.
        HOPEFULLY_THE_AGE_OF_EXORCISTS_HAS_COME_AT                                    = 10221,  -- Hopefully the age of exorcists has come at last, and hats off to Robertioux if it is so.
        SIGH_ALTANA_DAMN_THAT_STUPID_ELVAAN                                           = 10222,  -- ...<Sigh> Altana damn that stupid Elvaan.
        JEEPERS_CREEPERS_I_DIDN_T_KNOW_A_PIONEER                                      = 10223,  -- Jeepers creepers, I didn't know a pioneer was watching me!
        SORRY_I_SHOULDN_T_BE_SPEAKING_ILL_OF                                          = 10224,  -- Sorry, I shouldn't be speaking ill of my cohorts while others are within earshot.
        YES_I_WORK_ALONGSIDE_THE_OVERNIGHT_SENSATION_THAT                             = 10225,  -- Yes, I work alongside the overnight sensation that is Robertioux.
        HIS_FIFTEEN_MINUTES_OF_FAME_HAVE_TO_BE                                        = 10226,  -- His fifteen minutes of fame have to be up soon, though. I mean, how could someone as bumbling and bland as he possibly survive the scrutiny of the public eye?
        AND_YET_THERE_HE_IS_PLACED_ON_A                                               = 10227,  -- And yet, there he is, placed on a pedestal higher than the heavens. I'm envious of his situation, to say the least.
        I_KNOW_IT_S_THE_SOCIALLY_ACCEPTABLE_THING                                     = 10228,  -- I know it's the socially acceptable thing to be proud of your colleague's accomplishments, but...but...it's Robertioux.
        IF_HE_GETS_TO_BE_CALLED_A_GENIUS                                              = 10229,  -- If he gets to be called a genius, then I deserve to be called the oracle of the Adoulin islands! Robertioux's neither the hero Adoulin wants, nor the one it needs.
        COME_TO_THINK_OF_IT_FOR_A_WIMPY                                               = 10230,  -- Come to think of it, for a wimpy birdbrain like him to get any kind of praise, he must've been secretly training from sunset to sunrise.
        IF_ONLY_I_COULD_FIND_OUT_WHAT_SORT                                            = 10231,  -- If only I could find out what sort of regimen he used, then maybe my day would come as well...
        AHA_PERFECT_I_BELIEVE_THE_SCOUTS_COALITION_IS                                 = 10232,  -- ...Aha, perfect! I believe the Scouts' Coalition is going to write an article about his exploits.
        WOULD_YOU_MIND_ASKING_SOMEONE_THERE_WHAT_THEY                                 = 10233,  -- Would you mind asking someone there what they were able to dig up on him?
        MIND_ASKING_NOT_A_BIT_YOU_RE_A                                                = 10234,  -- Mind asking? Not a bit. You're a big girl; do it yourself.
