        HE_S_GOT_SOME_TWISTED_SENSE_OF_MODESTY                                        = 10248,  -- He's got some twisted sense of modesty. Ev'ry time I ask fah a word or two, he always gives the same-wame reply: I am hardly a worthy subject for your prose.
        YOU_D_THINK_HE_D_KNOW_BETTAH_IF                                               = 10249,  -- You'd think he'd know bettah. If he'd just oblige me, I could cast his ordah in a much prettiah lightaru than it is now.
