        AND_WHO_WOULDN_T_BE_I_PULLED_THAT                                             = 10262,  -- And who wouldn't be? I pulled that line right from one of the most hallowed novels on exorcism ever to be penned: Ergo Expulsion.
        YOU_HAVE_TERRIBLE_TASTE_HOW_COULD_YOU_YAWN                                    = 10263,  -- You have terrible taste, %. How could you yawn at one of the most famous lines in one of the most famous novels on exorcism: Ergo Expulsion?
