        TO_THINK_I_D_BEEN_LOOKING_AT_THIS                                             = 10270,  -- To think I'd been looking at this issue wrong the whole time.
        ONE_DOESN_T_SIMPLY_IMPROVE_WITHOUT_GRASPING_THE                               = 10271,  -- One doesn't simply improve without grasping the basics. And how could I ever hope to usurp Robertioux's fame if I only copy him!?
        I_VE_GOTTA_DO_THINGS_MY_OWN_WAY                                               = 10272,  -- I've gotta do things my own way, at my own pace, and conquer my own inadequacies! In fact, why don't I get started on my own personal training regime right now?
