        THE_STREETS_ARE_ABUZZ_WITH_ROBERTIOUX_S_LATEST                                = 10274,  -- The streets are abuzz with Robertioux's latest exploits. First an exorcism, then an undead vanquishing...the man's out prrrotecting our fair city while the Pioneers' Coalition lackeys flip through raunchy periodicals on the chamber pot.
        I_WOULD_DARE_SAY_THAT_HE_AIMS_TO                                              = 10275,  -- I would dare say that he aims to become a high exorcist himself. Oh, to see the look on Ingrid's face when...
        OH_HOW_LONG_HAS_IT_BEEN                                                       = 10276,  -- Oh, %! How long has it been?
        HAVE_YOU_SEEN_THE_ARTICLE_THE_SCOUTS_COALITION                                = 10277,  -- Have you seen the article the Scouts' Coalition penned on Robertioux?
        A_GLIMPSE_INTO_THE_WORK_OF_THE_FAMED                                          = 10278,  -- A glimpse into the work of the famed Robertioux, mere moments before banishing a vile skeleton from the land!
        EVEN_INGRID_HERSELF_BLUSHES_BEFORE_HIS_DIVINE_PROWESS                         = 10279,  -- Even Ingrid herself blushes before his divine prowess!
        TO_THINK_ME_FOLLOWING_IN_THE_FOOTSTEPS_OF                                     = 10280,  -- To think--me, following in the footsteps of one so grand!
        I_VOW_THAT_ONE_DAY_THOSE_REPORTERS_WILL                                       = 10281,  -- I vow that one day those reporters will be doodling the name Erfimia in their notebooks.
        WHAT_BETTER_FIRST_STEP_THAN_TO_VENTURE_TO                                     = 10282,  -- What better first step than to venture to the site of his latest banishing? And who better to accompany me than you, %?
        WILL_YOU_ASSIST_ERFIMIA_OF_COURSE_WHY_ME                                      = 10283,  -- Will you assist Erfimia? Of course. Why me?
        THIS_LL_BE_A_DAY_TO_REMEMBER                                                  = 10284,  -- This'll be a day to remember!
        LAYMEN_OFTEN_THROW_THE_WORD_UNDEAD_AROUND_WITHOUT                             = 10285,  -- Laymen often throw the word undead around without fully understanding it. The term encompasses the unliving as a whole, but there are many different types. Some are demons, others unholy spirits...yet there are also those who remain tethered to this world owing to some unfulfilled promise or deep-seated regret.
        AND_IF_SOMETHING_MANIFESTED_ITSELF_THERE_ONCE_IT                              = 10286,  -- And if something manifested itself there once, it's highly likely it'll do so again!
        WHY_WHAT_IF_THE_BANISHED_FIEND_WERE_TO                                        = 10287,  -- Why, what if the banished fiend were to make a reappearance? Surely you don't expect an inexperienced one such as myself to hold my own!
        AND_IF_SOMETHING_MANIFESTED_ITSELF_THERE_ONCE_IT_2                            = 10288,  -- And if something manifested itself there once, it's highly likely it'll do so again!
        THIS_ARTICLE_SAYS_THAT_ROBERTIOUX_QUELLED_THE_ABOMINATION                     = 10289,  -- This article says that Robertioux quelled the abomination in Yorcia Weald, somewhere around J-8.
        EVEN_THOUGH_RRROBERTIOUX_VANQUISHED_THE_IMMEDIATE_THREAT_YORCIA               = 10290,  -- Even though Rrrobertioux vanquished the immediate threat, Yorcia Weald is no place to let your guard down. Stay safe.
        ARAUSTOIX_HAS_ASSEMBLED_A_TWENTY_STRONG_FORCE_OF                              = 10291,  -- Araustoix has assembled a twenty-strong force of exorcists to banish the Blackthorn Coven once and for all. Good riddance, I say.
        OUR_BROTHERS_AND_SISTERS_ADVANCE_ON_THE_VELKK                                 = 10292,  -- Our brothers and sisters advance on the Velkk stronghold even as we speak. Hurry to Marjami Ravine, %, and join the call to arms!
        YOUR_AID_WOULD_BE_INVALUABLE_IN_STOPPING_THEIR                                = 10293,  -- Your aid would be invaluable in stopping their further incursion against us. We're counting on you!
        WELL_MET                                                                      = 10294,  -- Well met, %!
        I_MUST_EXTEND_MY_THANKS_FOR_YOUR_VALIANT                                      = 10295,  -- I must extend my thanks for your valiant service to our order--no, to all of Adoulin.
        I_WAS_HOPING_YOU_WOULD_STOP_BY_THE                                            = 10296,  -- I was hoping you would stop by the priory.
        NASHU_HAS_BEEN_LOOKING_FOR_YOU_AS_WELL                                        = 10297,  -- Nashu has been looking for you as well. To tell you the truth, I didn't think that he had it in him.
        THERE_S_NO_DENYING_IT_WITH_THESE_EVENTS                                       = 10298,  -- There's no denying it--with these events he's grown into a full-fledged exorcist of the Order of Weatherspoon.
