        HEHE_IT_S_MY_JOB_TO_BE_CURRRIOUS                                              = 10333,  -- Hehe, it's my job to be currrious. Besides, you're always talking to her out here.
        LATELY_SHE_S_BEEN_LOCKING_HERSELF_UP_IN                                       = 10334,  -- Lately she's been locking herself up in Celennia Memorial Library. Her nose has always been burrried in some book or other, but lately she's been taking out so many books that the staff has issued a formal complaint!
