        WHOOPS_IT_SEEMS_THEY_DO_NOT_ADD_ANY                                           = 12552,  -- Whoops, it seems they do not add any additional effects.
        BASED_ON_THE_STATE_OF_THEIR_EXPANSION_A                                       = 12553,  -- Based on the state of their expansion, a [Minor Attack Enhancement/Minor Magic Attack Bonus/Minor Gathering Fatigue Reduction/Minor Gathering Efficacy Enhancement/Moderate Attack Enhancement/Moderate Magic Attack Bonus/Moderate Gathering Fatigue Reduction/Moderate Gathering Efficacy Enhancement] will be bestowed upon you.
        BASED_ON_THE_STATE_OF_THEIR_EXPANSION_A_2                                     = 12554,  -- Based on the state of their expansion, a [Minor Defense Enhancement/Minor Magic Defense Bonus/Minor HP and MP Recovery Enhancement/Minor Enhancement to Max HP and MP/Moderate Defense Enhancement/Moderate Magic Defense Bonus/Moderate HP and MP Recovery Enhancement/Moderate Enhancement to Max HP and MP] will be bestowed upon you.
        BASED_ON_THE_STATE_OF_THEIR_EXPANSION_A_3                                     = 12555,  -- Based on the state of their expansion, a [Minor Accuracy and Magic Accuracy Enhancement/Minor Evasion and Magic Evasion Enhancement/Minor Critical Hit Rate Increase/Minor Haste Effect/Moderate Accuracy and Magic Accuracy Enhancement/Moderate Evasion and Magic Evasion Enhancement/Moderate Critical Hit Rate Increase/Moderate Haste Effect] will be bestowed upon you.
        BASED_ON_THE_STATE_OF_THEIR_EXPANSION_A_4                                     = 12556,  -- Based on the state of their expansion, a [Minor Save TP Effect/Minor Conserve MP Effect/Minor Fast Cast Effect/Minor Resistance Increase to All Status Ailments/Moderate Save TP Effect/Moderate Conserve MP Effect/Moderate Fast Cast Effect/Moderate Resistance Increase to All Status Ailments] will be bestowed upon you.
        BASED_ON_THE_STATE_OF_THEIR_EXPANSION_A_5                                     = 12557,  -- Based on the state of their expansion, a [Minor Crystal Obtainment Rate Increase/Minor Material Loss Rate Reduction/Minor Synthesis Skill Gain Rate Increase/Minor Synthesis Success Rate Increase/Moderate Crystal Obtainment Rate Increase/Moderate Material Loss Rate Reduction/Moderate Synthesis Skill Gain Rate Increase/Moderate Synthesis Success Rate Increase] will be bestowed upon you.
        BASED_ON_THE_STATE_OF_THEIR_EXPANSION_A_6                                     = 12558,  -- Based on the state of their expansion, a [Minor Combat Skill Gain Rate Increase/Minor Magic Skill Gain Rate Increase/Minor Experience Point Bonus/Minor Reward Obtainment Rate Increase/Moderate Combat Skill Gain Rate Increase/Moderate Magic Skill Gain Rate Increase/Moderate Experience Point Bonus/Moderate Reward Obtainment Rate Increase] will be bestowed upon you.
        WHAT_A_TRICKY_QUESTION_WELL_IT_IS_A                                           = 12559,  -- What a tricky question. Well...it is a thaumaturgical aura that grants multitudes of benefits to pioneers.
        WHAT_IS_TRULY_INTERESTING_IS_THAT_THIS_AURA                                   = 12560,  -- What is truly interesting is that this aura draws its powers from the various coalitions. The larger they grow, the more powerful the benefits each one will provide.
        THE_MORE_PIONEERING_FEATS_YOU_PERFORM_THE_MORE                                = 12561,  -- The more pioneering feats you perform, the more the coalitions develop, and the more beneficial Ionis becomes. Think of it as a virtuous cycle!
        YOU_HAVE_BEEN_IMBUED_WITH_THE_POWER_OF                                        = 12562,  -- You have been imbued with the power of Ionis!
        HELLO_THERE_ADVENTURER_MY_NAME_IS_OCTAVIEN_AND                                = 12563,  -- Hello there, adventurer. My name is Octavien and I hail from the Order of Orvail.
        SO_MY_ADVENTURING_FRIEND_HOW_LONG_DID_IT                                      = 12564,  -- So, my adventuring friend, how long did it take for you to reach Adoulin?
        HEH_HEH_HEH_I_ASSURE_YOU_MY_POWERS                                            = 12565,  -- Heh heh heh, I assure you my powers of perspicacity are not the same as omniscience. 'Tis but a trifle to tell outsiders from those of Adoulinian stock. One's gait, his/her] posture...or even the powers that lay dormant within him/her] provide ample evidence as to his/her] identity.
        PERHAPS_I_AM_RIGHT_ABOUT_SOMETHING_ELSE_AS                                    = 12566,  -- Perhaps I am right about something else as well. Do you happen to know of runes--magical emblems that have been passed down for generations?
        KNOW_YOU_OF_RUNES_OF_COURSE_SADLY_I                                           = 12567,  -- Know you of runes? Of course. Sadly, I do not.
        AHA_I_KNEW_IT_WHAT_AN_ENLIGHTENED_INDIVIDUAL                                  = 12568,  -- Aha, I knew it! What an enlightened individual I've come across. Still, possessing a mere passing knowledge of runes is insufficient to fully comprehend the mysteries contained within. Let me provide you with a more thorough explanation.
        RUNES_HAVE_EXISTED_SINCE_THE_AGE_OF_THE                                       = 12569,  -- Runes have existed since the age of the gods and are considered sacred, or so certain legends portend.
        STILL_MORE_LEGENDS_ASSERT_THAT_THE_SYMBOLS_FIRST                              = 12570,  -- Still more legends assert that the symbols first emerged from the north, on the continent of Rhazowa.
        HOWEVER_ALL_ACCOUNTS_SEEM_TO_AGREE_THAT_EACH                                  = 12571,  -- However, all accounts seem to agree that each letter in this mystical array harbors powers of thaumaturgic significance. Moreover, this special magic can only be released by a few talented individuals.
        THOSE_ABLE_TO_UNLOCK_THE_TRUE_NATURE_OF                                       = 12572,  -- Those able to unlock the true nature of these uncharacteristically powerful characters are dubbed rune fencers.
        NOW_AS_TO_WHY_I_ASKED_MY_PRIOR                                                = 12573,  -- Now as to why I asked my prior question and possibly bored you with a story as old as time immemorial:
        I_HAVE_REASON_TO_BELIEVE_YOU_ARE_ONE                                          = 12574,  -- I have reason to believe you are one of the chosen, one of those who can unlock the true potential of these runes. Call it runesmith's intuition.
        THAT_SHOULD_BE_SUFFICIENT_BACKGROUND_INFORMATION_AFTER_ALL                    = 12575,  -- That should be sufficient background information. After all, my true purpose isn't to flaunt my vast intellect, but to awaken the latent rune powers of the chosen, per the order of the Order of Orvail.
        BUT_I_DIGRESS_SHOULD_YOU_TRULY_WISH_TO                                        = 12576,  -- But I digress. Should you truly wish to walk the path of the rune fencer, I would be more than happy to guide you.
        THE_ROAD_IS_LONG_STRENUOUS_AND_ABOVE_ALL                                      = 12577,  -- The road is long, strenuous, and--above all else--steep. Many runesmith cragsmen have lost their foothold during their climb only to plummet to the darkest depths of concession, their days spent shrouded in shame.
        PROCLIVITIES_AND_PROPENSITIES_AVERSIONS_AND_ANTITHESES_THESE_ARE              = 12578,  -- Proclivities and propensities, aversions and antitheses...these are the cards you are constantly dealt to deal with your opposition!
        YET_THE_FIRST_STEP_STARTS_WITH_RUNIC_THEORY                                   = 12579,  -- Yet the first step starts with runic theory, then a hop to sparring, skipping to field practice, and finally a jump to applying your years of experience. The regimen is so harsh that many students often step down in dismay after the first few years.
