        YOU_ARE_CHARGED_WITH_COLLECTING_THE_PROPER_INGREDIENT                         = 12593,  -- You are charged with collecting the proper ingredient to create this ink. Keep in mind that I send you upon this task not because of my revulsion toward menial labor, but so that you may familiarize yourself with what will become your new essence.
