        AND_IT_REQUIRES_THAT_THE_WEARER_SWEAR_AN                                      = 13722,  -- And it requires that the wearer swear an oath to the higher power. But you would know all about that, wouldn't you? After all, you vowed [to bring harrrmony to nature in Adoulin/to prrrotect Adoulin's natural environment/to do everrrything possible to save nature].
